    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cooling_body",
      "x": 238,
      "y": 315,
      "width": 284,
      "height": 85,
      "text": "fastMode.ts manages cooldown timer:\n\n- Short delay <20s: keep Fast Mode, wait\n  (preserve prompt cache)\n- Long delay >=20s: triggerFastModeCooldown()\n  -> min 10 min cooldown (prevent flip-flopping)\n- Overage disabled -> permanently disable\n\nPurpose: prevent flip-flopping & respect global\nrate limits",
      "originalText": "fastMode.ts manages cooldown timer:\n\n- Short delay <20s: keep Fast Mode, wait\n  (preserve prompt cache)\n- Long delay >=20s: triggerFastModeCooldown()\n  -> min 10 min cooldown (prevent flip-flopping)\n- Overage disabled -> permanently disable\n\nPurpose: prevent flip-flopping & respect global\nrate limits",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#FFFFFF",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
